'''Aɣyul''', d aɣersiw i yellan s waṭas deg umaḍal, mecṭuḥ seddaw n uɛawdiw, imeẓẓuɣen-is d imeqṛanen. Aṭas n ccetlat n yiɣyal i yellan deg umaḍal, maca win yettwasnen aṭas gar-asen d aɣyul aqeddac (âne domestique s tefṛansist) i d-yekkan seg usegred n waɣyul azagir (âne sauvage).

==Amawal==

Awtem : Aɣyul.

Tawtemt : Taɣyult.

Aɣyul amecṭuḥ isem-is : Ajḥiḥ.

